Class BaseApplicationContextWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apereo.cas.web.BaseApplicationContextWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.springframework.beans.factory.Aware, org.springframework.context.ApplicationContextAware
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClearpassApplicationContextWrapper, DuoApplicationContextWrapper, GoogleAuthenticatorApplicationContextWrapper, OAuthApplicationContextWrapper, OpenIdApplicationContextWrapper, Pac4jApplicationContextWrapper, RadiusApplicationContextWrapper, RadiusMultifactorApplicationContextWrapper, SamlApplicationContextWrapper, SamlGoogleAppsApplicationContextWrapper, SamlIdPApplicationContextWrapper, SpnegoApplicationContextWrapper, WsFedApplicationContextWrapper, YubiKeyApplicationContextWrapper

    @RefreshScope
 @Component
public abstract class BaseApplicationContextWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.springframework.context.ApplicationContextAware
    Parent class for all servlet context initializers that provides commons methods for retrieving beans from the context dynamically.

    4.2
